		<td width="10%" nowrap="nowrap">Post subject:&nbsp;</td>
		<td><b>Version 0.81</b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Changelog:<br />0.81<br />Added option &quot;TV Aspect Ratio&quot; in the video settings that simulates the screen format of the old televisions (4:3).<br />Added option &quot;Interpolation&quot; which enables, regardless of the type of filter used, the bilinear interpolation of the image.<br />Set to &quot;1&quot; the default value for the delay of the turbo buttons.<br />Fixed a memory leak in version D3D9.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


